Day 20
Jack Frost wants to review all the cocoa breaks he actually took â€” including the cocoa type and the location he drank it in. How would you combine the necessary tables to show each logged break with its matching cocoa details and location?


SELECT cl.break_id as logged_break, ct.cocoa_name as cocoa_details, lt.location_name as location
FROM cocoa_logs cl
  JOIN cocoa_types ct ON cl.cocoa_id = ct.cocoa_id
  JOIN break_schedule bs ON cl.break_id = bs.break_id
  JOIN locations lt ON bs.location_id = lt.location_id


ANSWER


